presentation.pdf contains the solution to Question 15 from NCERT class 12 Probability Ex 13.1

solve.py contains python code for obtaining final state vector
sheet2txt.py was used to convert excel data to text used in latex matrices

table1.tex describes states in Markov Chain
table2 contains data for transition matrix. 
data_matrix.xlsx contains the same data with decimals, read by solve.py
table3 contains data for initial state vector. 
data_initial.xlsx contains the same data with decimals, read by solve.py
table4 contains data for limiting state vector

graph1.txt contains nodes and edges of the graph

